title: Reward weights council
body:
Background: https://snapshot.org/#/uniclynft.eth/proposal/QmVnkAaLyhBDNBbeBA1qcZEhWgz1xjRU6y5Xr52KZW6tDo

To make the council impartial, this proposal suggests Leia (representing Unicly devs) and Jeff (YGG) to start off as the first council members.

Please vote below if you are in favor or not.
